=== Overview

dbga or DebugAgent is an embedded webserver based tool that allows communication between a Windows PC based Tool FDK Tool and Audio Drivers/FW.

=== Options

--- true
use this option to enable DebugAgent

	--- parameters
		- func_test: true or false - enable or disable the DebugAgent functional and unit tests. 
		- mock_dev : true or false - enable or disable the Mocked Audio Driver tests.

	--- code dir
		- vendor/intel/tools/dbga
		- device/intel/sepolicy/debug_agent


--- false
use this option to disable DebugAgent

